  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.796554505096243         21.6754           499.85          2091.35
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.514320787408235        -13.9954          -322.74         -1350.35
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.174930899373824         -4.7601          -109.77          -459.28
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.048680079604225          1.3247            30.55           127.81
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.027200990192725         -0.7402           -17.07           -71.42
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.128781907725684          3.5043            80.81           338.12
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

